    "body": "Can you provide your code here? \n\nThe following code works well on OS X:\n1. Login in GitHub website, and quit application.\n2. Relaunch application, and my account still keeps login.\n\n```\nvar app = require('app');\nvar BrowserWindow = require('browser-window');\n\nvar mainWindow = null;\n\n// Quit when all windows are closed.\napp.on('window-all-closed', function() {\n  app.quit();\n});\n\napp.on('ready', function() {\n  mainWindow = new BrowserWindow({\n    width: 800,\n    height: 600,\n    'auto-hide-menu-bar': true,\n    'use-content-size': true,\n  });\n\n  mainWindow.loadUrl('https://github.com');\n  mainWindow.focus();\n});\n```\n"
